-- Hudson Pacific to buy California properties in $3.5 bln deal
-- By Sagarika Jaisinghani in Bengaluru
-- Mon Dec 08, 2014 08:22AM EST
-- None



Dec 8 (Reuters) - Hudson Pacific Properties Inc <HPP.N> said it would buy a portfolio of office buildings in California from a unit of Blackstone Group LP <BX.N> for $3.5 billion in stock and cash.

Hudson, a real estate investment trust focused on office properties, will pay $1.75 billion in cash and issue about 63.5 million shares and operating partnership units to Blackstone. [ID:nBw1DkX8ma]